Other Borrowed money with a Maturity Date More Than a Year are interest free loans from the Service Employee's International Union.  Therefore, PC line 2b is zero.^The Fair Value Option is used on PC Lince 2C.^The Bank's Stockholder Equity as of 9/30/22 decreased by 76,137,000 from 12/31/21.  This caused the Carrying Value of the Stock to decrease by 17,473,000.^The Bank had an After Dividend Net Income for 1/1-9/30/22 of 48,696,000.  Workers United owns 26.0920% of the Outstanding Stock and the amount shown on PI Line 7c is 12,706,000.^The Bank Value decrease of 17,473,000 and the Holding Company's share of the After Dividend Net Income of 12,705,000 causes an adjustment for balancing purposes of 30,478,000.  This affects PI Line 2d & PI-A Line 2g.^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^WWW.WORKERSUNITED.ORG^19103^^^^
